<scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
<head>Scope and Content
</head>
<p>Records, 1863-1926, for various railroads operating in Virginia consisting of articles of agreement, bills of lading, correspondence, envelopes, fliers, order forms, overcharge claims, receipts, and tickets regarding the operations and business of various railroads in Virginia, including the Baltimore and Ohio, the Norfolk and Western, and the Richmond and Danville Railroads.
</p>
</scopecontent>
